  - GEOSITE,category-ai-!cn,🤖 AI服务

  # ⑧ Apple Intelligence / Private Cloud Compute（高优先级）
  # 必须在 Apple 通用规则之前，确保 AI 功能走代理
  - DOMAIN,apple-relay.apple.com,🍎 Apple Intelligence
  - DOMAIN,apple-relay.cloudflare.com,🍎 Apple Intelligence
